<strong>using movable type trackback to post</strong><br>
<p>Movable Type users can use Trackback pings to write their latest entries to the Austin Stories database.</p>

<p>To send a Trackback ping, enter <em>http://www.austin-stories.com/ping.php</em> into your "URLs to ping" box. You may also configure a channel to ping Austin Stories automatically.</p>

<p>Your Trackback ping will be saved to the database, but it will not be published to the site. You must log back into your account to publish it. See <strong><a href="/index.php/help/topic/portal_post/{if $popup_flag==true}1/{/if}">posting and editing portal entries</a></strong> for guidelines on editing your ping.</p>

